org.tms.api.io

Interface ArchivalIOOption<T extends ArchivalIOOption<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of IOOption in this ArchivalIOOption
    All Superinterfaces:
    IOOption<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    org.tms.io.options.ArchivalIOOptions, TMSOptions, XMLOptions

    public interface ArchivalIOOption<T extends ArchivalIOOption<T>>
extends IOOption<T>
    An IOOption where the output can persist TMS-specific functionality. Elements that are supported include:
    • derivations,
    • validators,
    • descriptions,
    • display formats, and
    • units.
    Note: ArchivalIOOption methods affect both import and export operations.

    Since:
    "1.1"
    Version:
    "1.1"
